WEBVTT

00:00:02.037 --> 00:00:06.081
iz ir zent geven in a fabrik fa- hot zi gehat a fabrik mit trikotar?

00:00:07.285 --> 00:00:17.032
dort iz geven a, der balbos fun dem hoyz hot gehat a groyse fabrik oyf nalivkes fun tri- fun luksus vesh, trikotazh vesh.

00:00:17.545 --> 00:00:20.998
un s'iz geven geshafn SHOPn fun Tebetsn,

00:00:22.489 --> 00:00:31.730
un er hot nisht, un un s'iz gevezn zeyer a sakh fabrikantn fun Lozh vos zenen gekumen arayn un geblibn voynen oykhet in geto, in Varshe,

00:00:31.854 --> 00:00:35.513
raykhe mentshn, Korn, der, yener, farshidene.

00:00:35.513 --> 00:00:40.117
zenen zey alts in yenem gegnt geven kontsentrirt, s'zenen geven zayne bakante,

00:00:40.444 --> 00:00:44.364
dem fabrikant's. ober keyn fabrik hot er shoyn nisht gehat,

00:00:44.364 --> 00:00:51.592
ober m'hot im gekent, Nayfeld, Nayfeld hot er geheysn, als groyser fabrikant.

00:00:51.717 --> 00:00:57.194
flegn zikh tsun im vendn di vos hobn nisht gehat keyn dekung, zenen nisht geven in keyn fabrikn,

00:00:57.775 --> 00:01:00.134
u- un hobn nisht gehat keyn keyn kartn,

00:01:00.134 --> 00:01:04.687
keyn oysflug kartn oyf tsu lebn, oyf tsu kumen, oyf tsu oyf arbetn, b-

00:01:06.448 --> 00:01:10.762
az zey zey viln shafn a trikotazh, oyf triko.

00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:14.739
iz mentshn do- iz ver s'hot gekent hot gebrengt a mashin,

00:01:14.739 --> 00:01:23.624
nisht tsum undz iz undz punkt nor nokh frier m'ho- vos m'hot oysgearbet shukhvarg, Shults iz gevezn, geven shoyn groyse fabrikn,

00:01:23.624 --> 00:01:29.577
vos zey hobn aroysgefirt di arbeter, hobn zey gekrign a bisl zup, keyn gehalt nisht, ibern tog.

00:01:30.580 --> 00:01:34.576
in meshekh fun di tsayt iz shoyn amshpetstn der Nayfeld

00:01:34.576 --> 00:01:39.098
gevorn gebetn fun etlekhene fabrikantn fun Lodzh, raykhe,

00:01:39.098 --> 00:01:44.647
az zey ebn im finantsirn un er zol UNK oyfshteln a fabrik fun trikotazh.

00:01:44.957 --> 00:01:47.786
un demolts iz gevezn der rusishe front,

00:01:48.619 --> 00:01:51.971
iz vos hot men gebrengt? m'hot dokh gemuzt epes brengen,

00:01:52.382 --> 00:01:57.253
iz yeder eyner vos iz arayngeganen, ver s'hot nodl un mashinen, farshidene mashinen,

00:01:57.748 --> 00:02:04.104
un ikh bin dokh gevezn fun a f- a shnayderin, fun dem fakh, un zi hot mikh gekent,

00:02:04.414 --> 00:02:07.142
azoy zi hot mikh bakent mit dem Nayfeldn,

00:02:07.418 --> 00:02:16.856
un m'hot ongehoybn brengen vesh, oyf tsu makhn naye vesh. s'geven dray nodlen, farshidene farshidene mashinen, un mentshn hobn gebrengt

00:02:16.856 --> 00:02:20.290
abi s'zol hobn dekung, az zey zenen basheftikt.

00:02:20.290 --> 00:02:24.709
az zey zenen noyt- noytik, az m'darf zey nisht avekre- avekfirn. sof,

00:02:24.057 --> 00:02:27.797
ver s'iz nisht geven basheftikt hot men bald avekgef-

00:02:26.706 --> 00:02:33.917
hot men bald. zey hobn nisht gehat vos tsu bavayzn. un di oremkeyt iz geven groys, hobn zikh afile tsugeshtelt far dem broyt vos zey hobn geshribn.

00:02:33.917 --> 00:02:42.866
iz geven eyner bay undz vos hot ge- vos hot ge- gemoln, eyner a a trikotazhnik take, hot er gemoln a vog

00:02:43.007 --> 00:02:46.066
aza, un oyf eyn vogshol ligt a kop,

00:02:46.066 --> 00:02:53.278
a yid mit a bord, dem tsveytn sht- ligt a shtikl broyt mit a sloy s-, er hot gehaltn in eyn moln.

00:02:53.537 --> 00:02:57.263
a eyner v- vos oyf dey di opteylung fun di vesh.

00:02:57.263 --> 00:03:02.731
dos di ende iz gevezn az keyn naye, keyn shum naye vesh iz nisht geven.

00:03:02.731 --> 00:03:10.164
nor m'hot gebrengt fun front farblutikte, farloyzte, farkakte vesh,

00:03:10.164 --> 00:03:15.603
fun di soldatn fun front, fun di rusishn front, bloyz blut.

00:03:15.981 --> 00:03:23.535
un heys iz gevezn, fley, mit farshidene ge- dos alts hob- hobn undz gemakht.

00:03:23.575 --> 00:03:28.204
nor lomir zogn, s'hot badorfn aroys fun a, fun, zey hobn gegebn zek,

00:03:28.204 --> 00:03:31.680
in a zak iz geven lomir zogn fuftsik gatkes.

00:03:31.680 --> 00:03:37.575
yo, hobn undz tseharget, zey hobn koym gekrign tsen shtik, m'hot gehakt, vi s'nisht geganen.

00:03:37.699 --> 00:03:45.404
keyn nayes iz gornisht gevezn, s'geven a fiktsye. nor vos, der Nayfeld iz gevorn bakant.

00:03:46.305 --> 00:03:54.435
eyns hot er gehat a folks-doytsh, a Yan, vos iz gevezn in Poyln frier, an ongeshtelter in a groyser firme, a yidisher davke,

00:03:54.435 --> 00:04:07.595
hot zikh arumgedreyt lebn dem Tebesn. s'geven etlekhene Tebins in Tel-Avi- in ikh vil zogn in Tel-Aviv, in Varshe, oyf tsu ⟨lernen⟩ a shule iz vos iz geven, a handls-shule,

00:04:07.686 --> 00:04:12.152
oyf Leshno bay undz, un bay undz oykhet oyf Leshno, un an ander Nimo.

00:04:13.221 --> 00:04:19.183
alzo hot, er hot mikh a- a-, ikh hob dokh epes an anung in dos, oykh avekgezetst bay an OVERLOCK mashin,

00:04:19.183 --> 00:04:23.221
un m'hot gehakt. fun tsen por ge- gatkes iz aroysgeganen tsvey.

00:04:23.700 --> 00:04:30.174
fun di gatkes, do gemakht, do gemakht, un dos iz geven di bakantshaft fun di damke vos hot mikh bakent.

00:04:31.328 --> 00:04:37.214
nakher iz dos oykhet dos gevorn oysgenutst az m'zol ofitsyel gehern tsu Tebesn,

00:04:37.214 --> 00:04:39.793
fun di shnayders vos mayn man hot geshafn.

00:04:42.364 --> 00:04:47.555
un dos iz geven mentshn vos hobn gornisht farmogt, bundistn, komunistn,

00:04:47.578 --> 00:04:50.660
hobn nisht gehat nisht keyn mashin, nisht gornisht, nor fakhlayt.

00:04:51.088 --> 00:04:57.852
azoy az mayn man hot ibergenumen di gantse firung fun makhn iberkoyfn di groyse,

00:04:57.852 --> 00:05:01.944
eyner hot gedorfn an antsug, eyner hot badorfn a futer, eyner hot gedorfn dos,

00:05:01.944 --> 00:05:08.078
un er hot gehat a draysik mentshn vos hobn gornisht, hobn gornisht gehat tsu gebn,

00:05:08.078 --> 00:05:13.138
nor zenen geven fakhlayt, azoy az er hot, do iz geven di rikhtike shnayders.

00:05:13.347 --> 00:05:16.727
mayn bruder iz oykh geven a damen shnayder, far damen,

00:05:16.727 --> 00:05:20.276
hot er oykh gearbet mit mayn man, take oyf Leshno.

00:05:20.620 --> 00:05:23.972
un vi lang hot dos gedoyert, vi lang hot men dos gekent,

00:05:22.493 --> 00:05:25.676
dos hot, dos iz alts geven monatn eyns fun andern.

00:05:25.716 --> 00:05:27.904
un dos kind iz demolts shoyn gev-

00:05:26.037 --> 00:05:30.705
dos iz shoyn geven, dos iz shoyn geven nokhn KOSCIOL, nokhn kesl azoy gerufenem.

00:05:29.631 --> 00:05:35.801
ikh vil ir ir zolt mir nokh dertseyln vegn dem kestl, ober ersht, un dos kind iz demolts shoyn geven bay di goyim.

00:05:35.470 --> 00:05:40.630
dos kind iz avekgeganen take fun Leshno, hob ikh adurkh gegan nokh di hoypt gerikht,

00:05:40.630 --> 00:05:45.133
s'adurkh gegan oyf a tsveyter gas, dort take vu s'hot gevoynt Kshevitski noent,

00:05:45.342 --> 00:05:49.726
hob ikh aribergefirt fun, di arayngang iz geganen fun undz fun Leshno,

00:05:49.726 --> 00:05:53.396
ober s'shoyn geshtanen a v- oyfgeshtelt oyf undzer zayt,

00:05:53.396 --> 00:05:57.885
oyf di vu s'glaykhe numern, tsvey un fertsik, fir un fertsik,

00:05:57.885 --> 00:06:03.830
iz shoyn geshtanen a a heykh fun e- a a shtok, fun tsigl oyfgeboyt,

00:06:03.988 --> 00:06:12.217
oyf di zayt, un oyf yene zayt iz geven kimat leydik, oder s'hot zikh ver oysbahaltn, nisht keyn polyakn, nisht keyn yidn hobn gevoynt oyf Le- oyf Leshno,

00:06:12.274 --> 00:06:16.031
un in der heykh iz geven tsemo- tsehakte flesher,

00:06:16.712 --> 00:06:22.713
m'zol nisht kenen ariber shmuglen zikh. nor s'geven fun tsayt tsu tsayt az toyer iz geshtanen a vakh,

00:06:22.720 --> 00:06:27.475
un di yidishe p- a a politsyant, in aza vakh fun der fabrik,

00:06:27.475 --> 00:06:29.649
un m'hot gekent zikh aroysganvenen.

00:06:29.740 --> 00:06:35.398
alzo ikh hob dos kind shoyn aroysgefirt nokh a Zamenhof brik, nokhn gerikht adurkh.

00:06:35.398 --> 00:06:36.973
hoy- dos hoypt gerikht.

00:06:37.823 --> 00:06:46.237
vos iz nor geven in Varshe, iz gevezn oyf di gas, oyf Leshno, un s'adurkh geganen oyf a tsveyter gas, noent vu der Kshevitski hot gevoynt.

00:06:46.277 --> 00:06:48.954
iz m'adurkh geganen nokh a kleyn gesele.

00:06:50.496 --> 00:06:54.118
dortn hot mikh ge- opgevart di froy zayne, dem,

00:06:52.538 --> 00:06:53.578
zi al-

00:06:54.124 --> 00:06:57.226
un ikh hob ir gezogt, "ikh geb dir avek dos tayerste vos ikh hob,

00:06:57.226 --> 00:06:59.973
un vos ikh vel nor kenen, vel ikh vayter gebn."

00:07:00.199 --> 00:07:05.728
tsum sof hot men nokh dervust zikh der untergrunt az dort gefint zikh mayn Sare.

00:07:07.287 --> 00:07:11.466
un der u- un eyner vos hot oysgezen, vos ikh hob aykh dertseylt,

00:07:11.590 --> 00:07:15.864
vos er iz geganen tsu undz mit mir tsuzamen in eyn shule, nor in a hekhere klasn,

00:07:15.864 --> 00:07:21.323
vos hot oysgezen vi a goy, iz aro- iz iz geven in kontakt shoyn mit dem

00:07:21.323 --> 00:07:29.710
vu mayn Sare iz gevezn. ver hot oysgearbet afile far di untergrunt mentshn ken kartn, dos heyst pa- pasportn.

00:07:29.710 --> 00:07:31.563
dos hot geheysn ken-karte.

00:07:31.789 --> 00:07:33.571
vi azoy hot er geheysn?

00:07:33.510 --> 00:07:43.477
e- er hot geheysn Vroblevski. Vladislav Vroblevski.

00:07:43.146 --> 00:07:44.152
yo.

00:07:44.850 --> 00:07:47.943
er, der untergrunt fun der arisher zayt,

00:07:47.943 --> 00:07:54.533
iz adurkh geganen, er, der Zigmund, vos ikh hob aykh do gevizn mit dem m- militerishn hitl,

00:07:54.533 --> 00:08:08.734
in dem bukh hob ikh aykh ayn gevizn, ver iz gevezn eyn ofitsir in di poylisher armey, un er iz geve- m'hot im opgelozt, iz gefangener, er iz shoyn geven in Daytshland hot men im shoyn aroysgefirt, iz er tsurikgekumen, iz er gevorn a UNK,

00:08:08.734 --> 00:08:11.560
un azoy vi er hot gehat azan oyszen fun a goy,

00:08:11.560 --> 00:08:16.277
fun ts- ts- f- fun tsen goyim, not der aktsent, dos redn iz geven shvakh.

00:08:16.277 --> 00:08:21.871
iz az, flegt er kumen tsu dem Vroblevski, bin ikh eyn mol dortn gehat gevezn,

00:08:21.871 --> 00:08:24.537
trots dem vos s'iz gevezn vayt, iber dem Vaysl,

00:08:24.537 --> 00:08:28.494
ober ikh bin eyn mol dort geven, zey ikh ongekumen, hobn i- im shoyn gekent.

00:08:28.494 --> 00:08:32.483
Zigmund. er hot geheysn Zalmen, ober Zigmund hot men im gerufn.

00:08:32.522 --> 00:08:39.463
iz hobn di di tokhter fun do vu zi mayn tokhter, vu mayn tokhter iz geven fun dem Vroblevski,

00:08:39.463 --> 00:08:44.548
hot azoy vi er hot oyfgemakht di tir hot zi nokhgeshpet dem aktsent vi azoy er redt poylish.

00:08:45.043 --> 00:08:48.479
er hot nisht geredt mit dem rikhtikn aktsent vi a polyak.

00:08:48.655 --> 00:08:50.980
aktsent veyst ir vos zi heyst?

00:08:49.954 --> 00:08:51.146
yo yo.

00:08:50.980 --> 00:08:55.400
diktsye. di diktsye hot men derkent s'iz nisht keyn reyn poylishe.

00:08:51.253 --> 00:08:52.698
yo yo.

00:08:53.447 --> 00:08:57.524
un ven m'hot nisht gehat di rikhtike diktsye hot dos gekent zayn toyt.

00:08:57.328 --> 00:08:59.350
ober er hot dokh oysgezen

00:08:59.350 --> 00:09:05.743
a fakt er hot z- er iz ge- er hot er iz geven oyf der arisher zayt, er hot ale, er hot ayn geshafn gever,

00:09:00.265 --> 00:09:02.301
er hot zikh geretet.

00:09:05.901 --> 00:09:09.759
un er iz un ven s'iz oysgebrokhn der geto iz er gornisht geven in geto.

00:09:09.968 --> 00:09:13.742
vayl er iz gor shpeter ergets dershosn gevorn in a shtetl.

00:09:14.001 --> 00:09:16.745
vayl er hot gezen s- m'zol tsushteln gever.

00:09:16.684 --> 00:09:21.841
ir hot gehat kesher, ir hot gehat bakante in untergrunt?

00:09:22.017 --> 00:09:24.171
fil ale bakante.

00:09:24.210 --> 00:09:27.978
dos bukh vos er shraybt zenen do do alts bakante, fun Bund,

00:09:27.978 --> 00:09:31.714
der firer fun Bund zenen zeyer a sakh, er Zigmund,

00:09:31.078 --> 00:09:38.834
un demolts hot ir gevust, ven ir hot ge- ven ir ho- ir zent geven in geto hot ir gevust az s'iz do a untergrunt un az s'iz do,

00:09:37.879 --> 00:09:46.260
an untergrunt ho'mir gevust di gantse tsayt. iz geven a P.P.S., iz geven dos, zenen gevezn i Bundevtses, sotsyalistn.

00:09:47.430 --> 00:09:55.642
di tsienistishe organizatsyes hobn oykhet gehat bakantshaftn, ken zayn, ober zenen nisht geven azoy gebu- -bundn vi di sotsyalistn.

00:09:55.952 --> 00:10:00.941
s'geven a P.P.S.ishe poylishe partey, tsvey erley P.P.S. zenen gevezn.

00:10:02.618 --> 00:10:04.974
deye v- deye Zigmund,

00:10:05.149 --> 00:10:12.399
ober ven i- ven ikh hob, ven mayn man hot geshafn di grupe mit di gute shnayders, ze'mir geven oyf a tsveyter gas, nisht oyf Leshno.

00:10:12.928 --> 00:10:18.237
oyf Karmelitske. ot dos, do- dos Karmelitske hot ongemakht mayn shver.

00:10:18.767 --> 00:10:22.979
er hot iz geven a manufaktorist, dos hoyz iz gevezn zayns,

00:10:23.172 --> 00:10:27.519
un Ptashnik, hot men dortn nor gemakht,

00:10:27.913 --> 00:10:35.720
m'hot shoyn nisht gekent geyn oyf der arisher zayt a- a- a- arbetn di gute zakhn, az er hot zikh likvidirt, shoyn geven nokhn KOSCIOL,

00:10:35.777 --> 00:10:40.110
hot oy- iz er gekumen tsu geyn aroyf oyf Karmelitske,

00:10:40.110 --> 00:10:46.520
un dertseylt az er kumt yetst fun Treblinke, vi azoy s'zet oys.

00:10:46.628 --> 00:10:54.587
in droysn zet men gornisht, tsu geboyt a linye biz bizn toyer vos hot geshribn Treblinke,

00:10:55.842 --> 00:10:59.247
vos dort ineveynik in dem toyer hot zikh getun gornisht,

00:10:59.247 --> 00:11:05.015
nor goyim hobn im der- der der der vos hot gefirt dem o- dem di di ban,

00:11:05.089 --> 00:11:09.456
un vos hot ge- un goyim arum, hobn mit im geredt,

00:11:09.456 --> 00:11:12.626
az es filt zikh geferlekh a roykh,

00:11:12.750 --> 00:11:19.612
un u- un m'yogt iz er blaybt shteyn der der vos firt di ban,

00:11:20.344 --> 00:11:25.977
un az s'kumen aroys in droysn a bisl mentshn mit shablyes, mit farshidene zakhn, un m'shrayt

00:11:25.977 --> 00:11:30.429
"shneler! shneler! shneler! shneler! shneler!" m'yogt ale arayn, s'vert farhakt dos toyer.

00:11:30.553 --> 00:11:32.774
dernokhn kumt on a frishe ture.

00:11:32.950 --> 00:11:35.306
un dos hot er enk dertseylt?

00:11:34.806 --> 00:11:42.343
az er hot geredt, mit dem KOLEJARZ, un dem a KOLEJARZ heyst der vos hot gefirt der ban.

00:11:41.067 --> 00:11:42.310
di ban,

00:11:42.568 --> 00:11:44.435
un er hot im dos dertseylt,

00:11:44.779 --> 00:11:51.877
az er hot nokh nisht gezen, zogt er, keyn mol, nor di goyim zogn az s'shtinkt keseyder opge- brenekhts.

00:11:53.537 --> 00:11:58.419
un er iz epes arayn, un fun dortn hot er zikh epes arayn geshmuglt keyn Kaloshin,

00:11:58.419 --> 00:12:03.256
in a kleyn shtetl, hot er dortn getrofn eynem, hot er gezogt, ikh gleyb nisht,

00:12:03.256 --> 00:12:06.741
s'hot zikh a por aroysgeganvet, tsvishn ontuekhtser fun,

00:12:06.741 --> 00:12:11.319
hot zikh aroysgeganvet fun Treblinke, azoy hot men fun Treblinke nisht gekent aroys.

00:12:11.319 --> 00:12:13.834
s'geven Treblinke iz geven tsvey lagern.

00:12:14.952 --> 00:12:18.602
eyne fun lebedike, hot men ge- hot di gantse

00:12:18.602 --> 00:12:22.471
dos gantse lebn fun di vos m'hot arayngeyogt in Treblinke iz geven a sho.

00:12:23.541 --> 00:12:26.944
iz geven Treblinke eyns un Treblinke tsvey.

00:12:27.253 --> 00:12:31.022
in Treblinke eyns iz gezesn, m'hot oysgetun,

00:12:31.022 --> 00:12:35.314
der nokh hot men arayngeshikt dem m- mentsh, a kind, a man, a

00:12:35.708 --> 00:12:38.868
a froy, a z- bobe, a zeyde, ver veyst,

00:12:38.868 --> 00:12:44.088
un m'hot opgeshoyrn di hor, bay froyen ekstere, di lange hor,

00:12:44.196 --> 00:12:54.883
un bald fun danet, fun dem frizirer, iz gevezn a himl-shtrase, dos heyst a gas mit sh- mit drotn,

00:12:54.883 --> 00:12:58.756
hobn zey gerufn himl-shtrase, un s'geshtanen der Ivan

00:12:58.756 --> 00:13:09.851
mit a shabl un arayngeyogt "shneler! shneler! shneler! shneler!" er hot UNK geredt oyf ukrainish, ober di dem di daytshn hobn geshrign oyf oyf daytsh, "shneler! shneler! shneler!"

00:13:09.851 --> 00:13:12.050
shneler iz azoy gut vi oyf yidish.

00:13:11.753 --> 00:13:14.953
un dos hot men enk dertseylt ven ets zents,

00:13:13.693 --> 00:13:15.833
un dos hot er dertseylt, Zigmund.

00:13:15.833 --> 00:13:17.990
iz gekumen tsu undz in fabrik dos dertseyln.

00:13:16.360 --> 00:13:19.138
ven ets zents nokh geven in geto?

00:13:18.638 --> 00:13:22.484
ni- nisht geven shoyn keyn geto, s'shoyn geven nokhn KOSCIOL o-.

00:13:20.882 --> 00:13:23.508
dos iz shoyn geven nokhn oyszidlung?

00:13:22.562 --> 00:13:26.580
nokhn KOSCIOL oykhet. s'shoyn gevezn,

00:13:25.793 --> 00:13:28.369
vi azoy zents ets aygntl-

00:13:28.830 --> 00:13:30.455
ikh hob dokh gezogt aykh,

00:13:30.455 --> 00:13:36.823
az ikh hob gehat di bakantshaft vos m'hot gemakht di trikotazh, ho'mir shoyn gevoynt oyf Leshno,

00:13:32.003 --> 00:13:33.094
yo.

00:13:37.318 --> 00:13:47.625
un oyf Leshno iz gevezn nokh a Tebes, un bald lebn Leshno hot s'hot ge- ge- ge- ge- ge- gelontshet zikh mit dem

00:13:47.625 --> 00:13:59.143
mit mit mit Leshno iz gevezn sh- Novolipye, dort hot der men, der tsveyter man gevoynt. iz geven Shults, nokh aza groyse fabrik, dort hot men oysgearbet shikh,

00:13:59.143 --> 00:14:01.657
kozhukhes, futers,

00:14:01.657 --> 00:14:10.694
farshidene zakhn. do iz geven oykhet bay a Tebes hekher aroyf iz oykh geven o- ont- ontuekhtser un shukhvarg, farshidene.

00:14:10.694 --> 00:14:18.439
un bay undz iz faktish geven nor a ibergekoyft oyf tsu gebn gelt, oyf tsu makhn matones, un aroystsukrign dem tsaygenish.

00:14:18.439 --> 00:14:19.618
di ken-karte.

00:14:18.645 --> 00:14:22.874
un ayer eltern, un ayer shvestern, m'hot zey ale tsev-

00:14:21.227 --> 00:14:24.326
zey zenen sh- s'iz shoyn nisht geven keyn zeykher fun zey.

00:14:23.725 --> 00:14:25.946
ven hot men zey genumen?

00:14:25.041 --> 00:14:30.502
zey hot men ale genumen di tsaytn fun take fun fun fun fun KOSCIOL.

00:14:30.897 --> 00:14:32.494
ir vilt mikh dertseyln vi azoy,

00:14:31.251 --> 00:14:34.569
ikh hob zey nisht gezen, ikh hob keynem shoyn nisht gezen.

00:14:34.457 --> 00:14:37.657
ir hot gev- v- ir hot gevust fun dem KOSC-

00:14:35.824 --> 00:14:43.276
zey zenen dokh ge- alts noent fun ge- fun fun umshlags-plats hobn zey gevoynt. mayn dire afile iz oykh geven.

00:14:40.093 --> 00:14:47.158
un ir hot gezen un ir hot gezen vos hot zikh getun ven m'hot zey ale avekgenumen?

00:14:46.422 --> 00:14:51.468
ikh bin dokh geven gor in a shoyn an ander gegnt, vos iz gevezn in gantsn nisht bavoynt mer.

00:14:51.528 --> 00:14:59.872
iz geven a iz geven oyf di an- Zamenhof a yidishe gas, nokh dem E- Esperanto dokter a nomen.

00:14:59.978 --> 00:15:03.320
s'hot geheysn Dzhike, hot men es a nomen gegebn Zamenhof.

00:15:03.380 --> 00:15:07.080
dos iz gevezn fray, vild, s'heyst s'hot shoyn keyner nisht gevoynt.

00:15:07.080 --> 00:15:11.780
dos hot men badorfn zikh adurkh shmuglen dort, bin ikh shoyn geven vayt. ikh bin shoyn geven oyf di gas

00:15:11.780 --> 00:15:16.960
vu ikh bin antlofn mitn kind bald fun onheybn oyf Leshno tsu mayn shvegerin.

00:15:17.657 --> 00:15:23.675
un ayer man iz geven demolts mit aykh? nokhn kesl, ayer man iz geven mit aykh?

00:15:22.247 --> 00:15:26.578
yo yo. er iz gevezn oyf Karmelitske,

00:15:26.685 --> 00:15:30.141
do vi ikh dertseyl aykh iz gekumen er opzogn, un

00:15:30.141 --> 00:15:36.495
un un epes zey flegn aroyskrign fun a goy vos m'hot im gevolt likvidirn gute zakhn.

00:15:36.495 --> 00:15:43.352
dos heyst ven ikh hob mitgearbet in a tsu bay zey eyder s'gevezn private bashtelungen,

00:15:43.729 --> 00:15:47.734
iz iz far fliers, dos heyst luksus geshnitene,

00:15:47.734 --> 00:15:55.445
un m'hot gearbet shut- ikh hob gehat shu- shutfes mit a mit dem shutef vos mayn man iz gevezn mit im bay di fabrik in UNK.

00:15:55.445 --> 00:16:00.530
dos iz gevezn alts azelkhe partey mentshn, ober gute fakhlayt.

00:16:00.402 --> 00:16:03.146
vi lang zent ir geven in Leshno?

00:16:01.802 --> 00:16:03.433
dos iz geven nisht lang.

00:16:03.591 --> 00:16:07.482
dos iz gevezn nisht lang, biz bizn kesl.

00:16:08.400 --> 00:16:11.988
un un m'iz tsurikgeganen fun di selektsye fun kesl,

00:16:12.130 --> 00:16:16.241
ir zent geven bay di selektsye fun kesl? yo.

00:16:15.201 --> 00:16:17.636
yo, ikh hob nisht gevolt, ikh hob mikh bahaltn.

00:16:17.636 --> 00:16:20.286
nor mayn man, du geyst do vu ikh gey.

00:16:20.286 --> 00:16:23.348
zog ikh, Shloyme, zol der toy- un s'geven azoy.

00:16:23.348 --> 00:16:29.339
keygn iber undz oyf oyf oyf Karmelitske,

00:16:29.339 --> 00:16:33.169
hobn gevoynt yidishe politsey, yeder gehat dortn opgeteylt.

00:16:33.169 --> 00:16:39.742
iz aroyfgekumen shabes bay nakht a yidisher politsyant,

00:16:39.742 --> 00:16:47.139
tsu undz tsu keygn iber ariber, un gezogt, herst tsu a, s'iz do a frisher or- a frisher farordenung.

00:16:48.175 --> 00:16:52.905
biz tsen in der fri, biz nayn in der fri, ikh gedenk nisht tsi biz tsener, biz nayner,

00:16:52.905 --> 00:16:57.689
az m'vet gefinen vemen oyf dem plats un nisht oyf lebn di geslekh,

00:16:57.689 --> 00:17:02.614
di gasn fun umshlag-plats, vert dershosn oyfn toyt, oyfn le- ort.

00:17:02.755 --> 00:17:05.854
zog ikh tsu mayn, un er hot gevust vu ikh bahalt mikh.

00:17:07.518 --> 00:17:09.514
er hot epes ikh veys nisht vos,

00:17:09.943 --> 00:17:14.977
moyre gehat. un er iz geven shvakher vi ikh, er iz geven afile nisht in in di militer.

00:17:14.977 --> 00:17:21.820
er hot gehat epes a, zayn muter iz geshtorbn bay tsvey un fertsik yor oyf oyfn harts,

00:17:21.820 --> 00:17:31.723
un m'hot mayn man nisht genumen tsu militer, er hot gehat der OT C., dos heyst in fal fun a milkhome mit gever, ober geyn dinen nisht.

00:17:32.607 --> 00:17:40.059
vayl er gehat epes di z- tsv- odern tsvey ZYLES tsunoyf gevoksn in harts.

00:17:40.487 --> 00:17:42.573
iz er nisht gegan in militer arayn.

00:17:44.875 --> 00:17:49.909
er hot gefilt er vet say vi nisht kenen keyn tsu f-, er iz nisht geven azoy unternemerish vi ikh.

00:17:49.909 --> 00:17:51.754
nisht azoy energish vi ikh.

00:17:51.928 --> 00:17:56.912
ikh hob gezogt, s'iz toyt, fun der ershter minut on. gegn zayn viln avekgebn dos kind,

00:17:56.912 --> 00:18:01.695
un un ikh do hob ikh mikh oykh bahaltn. er hot mikh gefunen.

00:18:01.695 --> 00:18:04.885
hor er mikh ongenumen bay der hant, " do vu ikh gey geystu oykhet."

00:18:04.885 --> 00:18:09.728
zog ikh, "Godl, Godl, s'iz toyt, zey viln zikh nor laykhter makhn!

00:18:09.728 --> 00:18:15.567
az undz zo'mir kumen ahin, nisht zey zoln darfn in yeder hoyf geyn zukhn un un dos o!

00:18:15.567 --> 00:18:24.114
dos iz oyf toyt! dos iz nisht keyn ge-" du vey- ikh hob dokh, m'hot dokh shoyn gevust az s'iz toyt, vayl Zigmund iz dokh gekumen, er hot undz direkt dertseylt fun dortn.

00:18:24.114 --> 00:18:26.432
khuts vos ikh hob aleyn farshtanen.

00:18:26.539 --> 00:18:32.745
zey hobn geheysn shraybn mankhe ekster arayn briv, s'iz an arbets-lager, fun dortn fun Treblinke geneyt,

00:18:32.745 --> 00:18:35.409
tsu der mishpokhe arayn, tsu shikn keyn Varshe,

00:18:35.702 --> 00:18:42.395
az s'iz zey arbetn, un zey krign azoy fil un azoy fil broyt, un zey krign a zup un zey krign dos.

00:18:42.435 --> 00:18:49.331
zoln zey zikh lozn nemen, alts azelkhe farshidene, s'zol zayn zey laykhter ontsukumen tsu likvidirn.

00:18:50.451 --> 00:18:53.466
un ikh bin, fun der ershter minut on, toyt.

00:18:53.860 --> 00:19:02.201
afilek ven zey hobn geshmuest oyf oyf oyf zumer-voynung az s'vet zayn a blits-milkhome, ikh hob gezogt az s'vet zayn a gresere milkhome.

00:19:02.201 --> 00:19:06.006
alts oyf shvarts, alts oyf rikhtik rikhtik vos s'iz.

00:19:06.006 --> 00:19:10.765
alzo mayn man hot mikh ge- gevust vu ikh bin bahaltn, un ikh hob nisht gevolt geyn.

00:19:10.765 --> 00:19:14.171
zog ikh, "du vilst geyn, gey, ikh vel dikh nisht haltn,

00:19:14.363 --> 00:19:21.411
i- zol men mir, ts- zol der toyt tse-, s'iz toyt! zol der toyt kumen tsu mir, lomir mikh do dershisn, zoln zey mikh khapn!"

00:19:22.733 --> 00:19:27.514
s'hot nisht geholfn, er hot mikh nisht opgelozt di hant un m'iz geganen tsuzamen mit ale

00:19:27.514 --> 00:19:30.759
tsu di gegnt fun umshlag-plats.

00:19:31.137 --> 00:19:34.742
dort arum un arum in di gasn. ikh hob gekent ale gasn.

00:19:31.170 --> 00:19:37.138
ven ven, ir gedenkt di dat- ir gedenkt ven dos iz geven, velkhe datum?

00:19:36.942 --> 00:19:39.939
ikh hob farshribn, ober ikh gedenk nisht genoy,

00:19:41.127 --> 00:19:46.251
ikh hob alts farshribn, afilek ikh tref ze ikh dokh nisht ibertsuleyenen. ikh hob es nokh farshribn nokh.

00:19:47.522 --> 00:19:49.574
s'iz zumer, vinter?

00:19:49.395 --> 00:19:54.620
s'iz neyn, s'iz geven far di yontoyvim. s'hot gekent zayn oygust.

00:19:51.910 --> 00:19:52.866
far di yontoyvim.

00:19:57.478 --> 00:20:04.120
ikh hob farshribn, ober ikh ze dokh nisht. ikh ken dokh nisht azoy fil gedenken in kop. der kop arbet dokh shoyn nisht oykh azoy gut.

00:19:59.436 --> 00:20:00.628
nisht vikhtik.

00:20:04.195 --> 00:20:09.014
ikh farges mankhe mol. dafke di dem onfang farges ikh, nisht dem sof.

00:20:10.236 --> 00:20:16.456
alzo, m'iz v- der sof iz gevezn az dafke dort in yenem gegnt m'iz gekumen

00:20:16.648 --> 00:20:21.235
hot er mikh nisht gezen keyn dray nokh anand, m'iz gelegn untern frayen himl,

00:20:21.235 --> 00:20:27.763
un dort iz geven a gegnt vos s'nisht geven keyn asfalt di vegn, nor kaylekhike shteyner.

00:20:28.343 --> 00:20:35.711
oyf di shteyner ze'mir azoy ge- -legn, nor azoy o, azoy gezesn, nisht vikhtik.

00:20:35.869 --> 00:20:44.418
s'nisht vikht- s- shtert, oy SLICHA! SLICHA. ikh hob fargesn.

00:20:44.813 --> 00:20:51.219
HAIKAR, azoy gezesn, nor shtendik hob ikh mit zikh getrogn azoy, a plet-zak,

00:20:51.934 --> 00:20:59.167
mit a lekht, a sher, a tsentimeter, a nodl mit bayvl, un a laterke.

00:21:00.051 --> 00:21:04.469
un efsher a por maytkes, un efsher a shtikl broyt. a fuln plet-zak.

00:21:04.469 --> 00:21:11.942
mit dem plet-zak hob ikh mikh gevalgert a in etlekhene UNK fun er hot mikh afilek nisht gezen gantse dray tog.

00:21:12.066 --> 00:21:16.408
dray tog un dray nekht. oyfn dritn tog hot men undz gerufn,

00:21:16.408 --> 00:21:21.560
iz punkt fun di gas vos mayne eltern hobn gevoynt, oyf Niske-Zamenhof, in Rok.

00:21:22.444 --> 00:21:29.087
bin ikh azoy gezesn oyf di knien, un s'gevezn un rekhts iz gevezn an otshered mentshn oyf kontrol,

00:21:29.262 --> 00:21:34.523
nisht, a por meter fun umshlag-plats, un in tsveyter zayt. un do iz geshtanen Brant,

00:21:34.523 --> 00:21:36.388
azoy farkatshet di arbl,

00:21:36.388 --> 00:21:42.620
in in eyn hant a flash bir, a hits iz gevezn, azoy az s'zikher geven amhekhstns y- oygust.

00:21:43.453 --> 00:21:46.754
iz dort geven a shtuperay, s'hot zikh der oylem geshtupt.

00:21:46.963 --> 00:21:53.178
azoy vi ikh ze az er k- er dreyt zikh oys azoy oyf tsu zogn, "rekhts, links, rekhts, links,"

00:21:53.178 --> 00:21:55.988
tsum umshalg-plats hot men badorfn geyn links,

00:21:55.988 --> 00:21:59.717
un tsu di gute vos darfn nokh tsurikgeyn tsu der arbet oyf rekhts.

00:21:59.717 --> 00:22:04.979
ikh bin punkt gevezn epes oyf rekhts noent, nor gants vayt in dem tor,

00:22:05.374 --> 00:22:10.667
un azoy vi er hot zikh ibergedreyt, hob ikh mikh gegebn a heyb oyf, ikh bin shoyn oyf der rekhter zayt.

00:22:11.618 --> 00:22:18.969
mayn man iz nokh nisht geven. nor mayn shver, der tate fun fun mayn man, iz shoyn yo geshtanen,

00:22:19.110 --> 00:22:23.137
un gezogt azoy: "m'hot zey in der erd, m'vet zey iberlebn."

00:22:23.565 --> 00:22:25.106
geven aza vitsele.

00:22:25.106 --> 00:22:30.295
m'hot zey in tha- m'hot zey iberlebn, geb a kuk mayn der shver mayner shteyt shoyn

00:22:30.295 --> 00:22:34.697
kimat in der ershter reye oyf tsu geyn gut tsurik in der f- tsu der arbet.

00:22:35.935 --> 00:22:42.223
un ikh shtey azoy, efsher in a halber sho arum her ikh vi der vos er makht lekher

00:22:42.432 --> 00:22:49.479
sh- vil zikh rateven un s'shteyt der goy vos flegt aroysgebn di arbet, di gute, di far di far di fliers,

00:22:49.485 --> 00:22:56.921
iz shraybt azoy, "panye Lestinski, UNK!"

00:22:57.484 --> 00:23:03.396
er hot gevolt oyf zikh tsien di oyfmerkzamkeyt, hot er geshrign, oyf mayn man ongevizn,

00:23:03.396 --> 00:23:07.598
un der Brant, der der daytsh, iz geven oysgedreyt dort ahin,

00:23:07.598 --> 00:23:13.301
hot der goy, der vos flegt ge- gebn arbetn, gefirt tsu UNK arbetn oyf der poylisher zayt,

00:23:13.301 --> 00:23:16.867
un dernokhn hot er ar- arayngegebn ineveynik, un- undz tsu arbetn

00:23:17.380 --> 00:23:26.689
hot er ho- hot er bay mayn man zikh dernentert un ikh geb a kuk, efsher in a halber sho arum iz er hersht ongekumen, bafrayt gevorn.

00:23:26.695 --> 00:23:28.362
m'iz aheymgeganen,

00:23:28.362 --> 00:23:34.215
aheymgeganen, nisht do vu mayn voynung oyf Karmelitske fun vant ikh vin gekumen, fun vant zey hobn ge-

00:23:34.356 --> 00:23:39.159
zogt er kum- un in Varshe iz geven azoy,

00:23:39.452 --> 00:23:43.456
di oyf di shtign iz nisht geven keyn ayzn, nor bloyz holts.

00:23:43.456 --> 00:23:49.470
alts fun holts. un dos alts iz farbrent gevorn, vayl s'nisht geven mit vos tsu heytsn,

00:23:49.678 --> 00:23:57.159
un dafke iz dos geven nisht keyn orem hoyz, iz es oykhet nisht geven di po-, dos heyst a porentsh, di onhalt oyf aroyftsugeyn oyf di shtign.

00:23:57.159 --> 00:24:00.472
un ir oryentirt zikh den nisht?

00:23:58.622 --> 00:24:00.202
yo yo zikher.

00:24:00.529 --> 00:24:06.086
alzo, un er kumt aroyf, der SHOP iz geven der oyf dem tsveytn shtok,

00:24:06.086 --> 00:24:10.597
un er zogt, "m'hot zey in der erd, m'vet zey iberlebn," un get a fal arop, mayn shver.

00:24:10.688 --> 00:24:15.204
mayn der tate mayn man's. arop fun tsveytn shtok.

00:24:15.295 --> 00:24:19.864
un er hakt zikh oys ale tseyn. un s'nishto ver s'zol rateven.

00:24:19.864 --> 00:24:25.768
er hot zikh op gemordevet a gantsn vinter, biz dem biz tsu dem oyfshtand.

00:24:26.635 --> 00:24:31.928
un dernokh iz er nokh mit mayn geforn keyn Ponyatov, un er iz dort geshtorbn normal.

00:24:31.933 --> 00:24:34.509
vayl s'nisht ver s'zol rateven di tseyn.

00:24:36.625 --> 00:24:38.931
un ir zent geblibn demolts in,

00:24:38.430 --> 00:24:48.347
un ⟨rikh⟩, ikh bin geblibn ikh hob ale demolts fun Karmelitske hob ikh gefirt oyf tsu Tebesn oyf Leshno.

00:24:48.910 --> 00:24:51.098
far gut, far di gute shnayders.

00:24:53.230 --> 00:24:58.905
dortn vu ikh hob gehakt bloyz di gatkes, hot men gemakht far gute shnayders. zey flegn brengen

00:24:58.905 --> 00:25:02.910
di groyse un di gelter hobn gegebn di raykhe, di lodzher,

00:25:03.304 --> 00:25:06.082
un m'hot keseyder azoy gemakht matones,

00:25:06.848 --> 00:25:17.287
iz dos gevezn a gantsn, biz ven, a gantsn vinter.

00:25:19.167 --> 00:25:23.633
alts azoy vi m'ho- un undz hobn ongehoybn trakhtn vegn rateven zikh.

00:25:24.043 --> 00:25:29.001
gelt hobn mir gehat, Kshevitski hot gehat undzer gelt, un m'iz geven in kontakt.

00:25:29.001 --> 00:25:33.718
er flegt aroy- durkh tsu shpatsirn oyfn tsveytn trotuar vu s'hot shoyn nisht gevoynt keyner,

00:25:33.718 --> 00:25:36.389
hot men undz im gezen vi er geyt ariber.

00:25:36.615 --> 00:25:44.624
un afilek etlekhe mol hot der goy vos hot gehat dos kind adurkh shpatsirt un m'hot dos gezen. a zuntik flegt er azoy adurkh shpatsirn.

00:25:44.142 --> 00:25:45.891
mitn kind.

00:25:44.783 --> 00:25:45.958
mitn kind.

00:25:46.707 --> 00:25:54.278
un dos iz geven dos eyntsike, dos eyntsike kontakt vos ets hots gehat, vos ets hots gevust az dos kind lebt?

00:25:46.858 --> 00:25:49.700
oyf di oyf di zayt dos hot keyner nisht gevoynt.

00:25:53.040 --> 00:25:54.786
dos iz, yo.

00:25:54.786 --> 00:25:57.770
er er Kshevitski hot dokh dos alts geshafn.

00:25:57.878 --> 00:26:00.521
vi alt iz dos kind geven demolts?

00:25:59.920 --> 00:26:05.650
dos kind iz shoyn alt geven demolt f- f- fir yor geendikt, finef yor.

00:26:06.687 --> 00:26:09.735
zi iz dokh geven finef yor in der milkhome un zi iz geven a por monat.

00:26:12.610 --> 00:26:21.904
ober zi, ikh m- mayn bruder hot ir oyfgeneyt azan ekstere, aza goyishk mantele, m'hot ir gemakht azelkhe, fun di lokn hot men gemakht azoy dine tsepelekh,

00:26:21.904 --> 00:26:27.271
azoy vi di shikselekh, un m'hot ir un a kapelitshl ongetun azoy vi a g- azoy vi a shiksl,

00:26:27.271 --> 00:26:31.976
un ikh hob ir adurkhgefirt nokh der nokh dem gerikht fun danet.

00:26:31.999 --> 00:26:41.240
un az s- s'flegt zayn a a ikh hob ir a por vokhn gehaltn bay zikh, vayl m'hot dokh geshnitn di gatkes, mit di layz, mit di di alding, mit di flign,

00:26:41.432 --> 00:26:46.103
az s'flegt zayn a a selektsye, m'hot gezukht,

00:26:46.103 --> 00:26:49.917
iz ikh hob dokh gehat vos zikh tsu bavayzn, dos kind iz geven umlegal,

00:26:49.917 --> 00:26:57.575
hob ikh ir arayngeleygt in a zak azelkhn mit di shmates, ikh hob ir aroysgenumen iz zi geven tsebisn azoy royt.

00:26:57.632 --> 00:27:08.915
un zi hot nisht geveynt. s'hot nisht al- nisht ale hobn dos alts ibergelebt in azelkhe pletser.

00:27:09.799 --> 00:27:15.851
a fakt az s'nishto keyner. fun mayn mishpokhe keyner nisht geblibn.

00:27:19.654 --> 00:27:22.061
vos i- s'arbet yetst vayter?

00:27:21.038 --> 00:27:22.230
yo yo.

00:27:24.683 --> 00:27:29.655
fun ayer mishpokhe hot men zey genumen ven s'iz geven di s- nokh frier.

00:27:27.140 --> 00:27:31.376
in in nokh firer, nokh nokh nokh frier farn farn KOSCIOL.

00:27:33.778 --> 00:27:39.425
ir zogt ir hot geprubirt tsu klern zikh tsu rateven ven ir zent geven in Leshno.

00:27:40.225 --> 00:27:44.033
yo. hot men ongehoybn klern vegn rateven zikh faran.

00:27:44.089 --> 00:27:50.074
iz geven eyner vos er hot gehat gelt a sakh, un ikh hob gehat a sakh gelt, hob ikh tsugenumen der goy

00:27:50.074 --> 00:27:56.994
farn kind, ober s'nokh geblibn genug bay Kshevitskin, ikh hob nokh dernokh dem geshikt ahin keyn Ponyakov.

00:27:57.758 --> 00:28:05.784
iz hob ikh ong- hot men ongehoybn klern vos m'tut vider do.

00:28:06.702 --> 00:28:12.922
a kh- shvegerin fun dem Vroblevski vu dos kind iz geven iz gevezn on a man.

00:28:13.182 --> 00:28:19.228
un er hot gehat eyn shtibele unter unter Varshe. hot dos geheysn Vlokhi.

00:28:19.228 --> 00:28:25.784
oyf poylish Vlokhi iz Italye, zogt men Vlokhi oyf poylish.

00:28:25.784 --> 00:28:28.278
nor dos iz gevezn unter di shtot shoyn.

00:28:28.858 --> 00:28:33.800
hot zi gehat eyn shtibele un hot, der man, keyn man hot zi nisht ge-, zi hot zi iz geven ge-

00:28:33.938 --> 00:28:40.178
z- bay zey iz dokh nisht faran keyn getn, zi hot ge- nisht gevoynt bay im di muter, un zi iz geven an oreme, hot nisht mer gehat vi eyn shtibl,

00:28:40.384 --> 00:28:47.347
un hot gearbet in a hotel, als ro- roymike, tsi vos, ikh veys nisht.

00:28:47.539 --> 00:28:56.763
alzo, a- der yungster zun hot khasene gehat, un eyn tokhter iz geven oyf arbet in Daytshland, zi hot nisht gehat mer vi di eyne di tokhter, ikh hob ir nisht gekent,

00:28:57.563 --> 00:29:06.726
nor der der yingsterer zun hot khasene gehat un er iz geblibn in dem shtibl, hobn zey gedorfn voynen ale tsuzamen. zi hot azoy veynik fardint, zi iz geven a roymike in a hotel,

00:29:06.878 --> 00:29:11.867
on a man, un s'geven nokh a zun, der eltster iz geven nokh a zun mit ir.

00:29:12.717 --> 00:29:19.066
alzo, er hot ir gege- iz iz er hot ir dertseylt az er hot a kind, der Vroblevski,

00:29:19.066 --> 00:29:23.961
un er hot gekrign dos, er hot yents, ir farshtey- er hot zikh a bisl,

00:29:23.961 --> 00:29:27.243
