00:29:31.397 --> 00:29:35.947
u- undz ikh mit mayn man un nokh eyner hobn gezolt zayn in di dire.

00:29:36.088 --> 00:29:40.692
gekoyft azoy vi a BAYIT MESHUTAF. Pulseskego nayntsn.

00:29:40.692 --> 00:29:44.942
UNK azoy ikh darf epes gedenken nisht, nor dos gedenk ikh.

00:29:45.032 --> 00:29:48.134
